Source: pgelog
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/anfiau/pgelog

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pgelog
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pgelog
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${postgresql:Depends}, postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-variables
Description: Extended PostgreSQL logging via pseudo-autonomous transactions
  pgelog writes extended log records through pseudo-autonomous transactions.
  It also requires the dblink extension at runtime.
